response.original_title: Why Is My Money Pending in Robinhood? How to Resolve It Efficiently
response.overview: Your money may be pending in Robinhood due to bank processing delays, failed transfers, or system errors (+1☆(877)☆496☆4626). Usually, transfers take 1–5 business days, but Instant Deposits are faster. To resolve it, check the “History” tab in your Robinhood app, ensure your bank account is linked correctly, and contact Robinhood support if delays persist +[A]1-(877) 496-4626[A].
